Manage Video Files

Video files can be uploaded and viewed through the ConservationSpace.

Upload Video File

To upload a video file:

  1. Select the Create/Upload button
  2. Select the context you want the Image to be uploaded

    Note: You can upload the video file in the context of a cultural object or in the context of project or any conservation activity. Uploading a video in the context of another system objects means that this Image will be part of that context and the permissions on that Video will depend on this context.

     

  3. Select "Upload" option
  4. Select "Select file.." option and chose the file from you local drive
  5. "Video" as a type will be recognized automatically if you are uploading video file types

Actions on Video Files

 

To view actions available on the Video select the Action option. A list with all actions will be displayed.
